  <h1>A6  Security Misconfiguration</h1>
  <p class="muted">Exposed debug pages, default credentials, or unnecessary services can be abused.</p>
  <h3>Mitigations</h3>
  <ul><li>Disable debug mode in production.</li><li>Harden server config and remove default accounts.</li></ul>
  <h3>Where to patch</h3>
  <p>Ensure <code>debug=False</code> and no sensitive info is exposed in error pages.</p>
